code: import axios from"axios";const API=axios.create({baseURL:"https://fitnesstrack-vtv1.onrender.com/api/"});export const UserSignUp=async data=>API.post("/user/signup",data);export const UserSignIn=async data=>API.post("/user/signin",data);export const getDashboardDetails=async token=>API.get("/user/dashboard",{headers:{Authorization:`Bearer ${token}`}});export const getWorkouts=async(token,date)=>await API.get(`/user/workout${date}`,{headers:{Authorization:`Bearer ${token}`}});export const addWorkout=async(token,data)=>await API.post(`/user/workout`,data,{headers:{Authorization:`Bearer ${token}`}});
